.fvmrc
analysis_options.yaml
**/ios/Flutter/Generated.xcconfig
**/ios/Flutter/flutter_export_environment.sh
**/ios/Runner/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.*
test/

# Build / IDE artefacts.
build/
*.iml

# `example/pubspec.lock` cannot be excluded — pub always re-includes it in the tarball
# (verified empirically against the dry-run: every other `example/...` pattern below
# works, but this one is silently overridden). pub.dev needs the lockfile to render the
# example's static analysis. Leaving the file as-is.

# Internal contributor / AI-agent docs — not useful to pub.dev consumers.
# AGENTS.md / CLAUDE.md are root symlinks into .ai/; .ai/ itself is auto-excluded by
# pub's hidden-path rule, but pub follows symlinks before that check, so the symlink
# targets need explicit entries.
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
APPENDIX.md
CODESTYLE.md
example/AGENTS.md
example/CODESTYLE.md

# Example platform dirs — pub.dev only renders example/lib/ + example/pubspec.yaml +
# example/README.md for the "Example" tab. Platform scaffolding adds bloat with no
# pub.dev-side benefit.
example/android/
example/ios/
example/devtools_options.yaml